# Moving by Character and Line

```
                   Previous Line C-p
                           ^
                           |
Previous Character C-p <---+---> Next Character C-f
                           |
		           v
                     Next Line C-n

```

# Moving by Word and Sentence


```
            Backward Sentence M-a
                      ^
                      |
Backward Word M-b <---+---> Forward Word M-f
                      |
		      v
            Forward Sentence M-f

```

# Moving to Beginning of Line and Buffer

```
                Buffer Start M-<
                       ^
                       |
Line Beginning C-a <---+---> Line End C-e
                       |
		       v
                 Buffer End M->
```

# Moving by Page

```
Back Page C-x
     ^
     |
     |
     v
Forward Page C-x ]

```

# Moving by Screen


```
Previous Screen M-v
       ^
       |
       |
       v
Forward Screen C-v
```

# Centering Point

```
Center Cursor C-I

```

# Searching

```
Reverse Search M-r
      ^
      |
      |
      v
Forward Search M-s
```

To repeat the search type `C-r`

# Going to a line number

```
M-g M-g
```